      "content": "## Feature Architecture\n- **AI Coaching Module**: Split into separate components (Feb 14, 2026)\n  - `quick-practice.tsx` — Quick Practice (video record + AI analysis)\n  - `mock-interview.tsx` — AI Video Interview (separate, full interview flow)\n  - `ai-coaching-progress.tsx` — Progress tracking\n  - Main `ai-coaching.tsx` — Router component\n- **Quick Practice Status**: Known issue — \"Load failed\" during AI analysis step (video records but analysis API crashes)",
